These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, turquise, black, lilac
4 different games are played: poker, mah-jongg, billiard, domino
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, rock, jazz, folk
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, motorbike, taxi
 1. the fan of rock is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
 2. the person driving the airplane is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the fan of dubstep is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 5. the person driving the airplane is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
 8. the person playing domino is between the person driving the jet-ski and the fan of rock##2
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person playing billiard##1
10. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
11. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
12. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
13. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
14. the person who likes turquise is the person driving the motorbike##1
15. the person who likes turquise is not the fan of rock##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Color         | green     | turquise   | lilac | black |
| Game   | mah-jongg | domino   | poker   | billiard  |
| Music-Genre         | rock  | jazz  | folk  | dubstep |
| Transport     | airplane    | motorbike | jet-ski     | taxi    |

