4 different games are played: canasta, billiard, domino, poker
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, boat, bus, roller
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the person driving the bus is between the owner of the dog and the person driving the boat##2
 2. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
 4. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person driving the boat##8
 6. the person playing poker is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the person driving the van is the owner of the frog##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
13. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
14. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
15. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
17. the person watching comedy movies is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8
18. the person playing billiard is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
