 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the bartender##5
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the person who likes light-blue##8
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
 7. the manager is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
 9. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes white##1
10. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
11. the person who likes light-blue is not to the left of the firefighter##8
12. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3

.:: Answer ::.
