11. the musician is on the right of the freelancer##1
12. the manager is not the person who growsorchid##6
13. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
14. the farmhouse house is on the left of the victorian house##1
15. the person playing go is not to the right of the manager##8

