 3. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5
 4. the person watching animation movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person drinking milk##7
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is not to the left of the aristoff-smoker##8
 8. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the guinea-pig##7
 9. the person watching family movies is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8
11. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
12. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
13. the bluemaster-smoker is the owner of the rat##1
14. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
15. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
16. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the owner of the dog##8

.:: Answer ::.
