House: ranch-style, tower, cape-cod, art-deco
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, november, september
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person traveling to venice is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person traveling to prague is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
 7. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the person traveling to nizza is not to the right of the tower house##8
11. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| City      | prague   | paris     | venice    | nizza |
| House   | ranch-style  | art-deco      | cape-cod     | tower     |
| Birthday         | march | november  | september     | june  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

